<br>
1. UrC has taken Aary, while many of you said they should not be in NToV and had no chance at killing him.  So that's positive for UrC.<br>
<br>
2. I feel that a lot of people posting call UrC something close to immature and not responsive to the rules of NToV yet when they post they act immature themselves.  Making fun of the way a person types, what they've done in their EQ life...don't be a fool and be a hypocrit, no one likes hypocrits.<br>
<br>
3. Sure, people make mistakes.  Everyone makes mistakes, but its the good person that can push things aside and not blow up over simple issues.  I'm sure that UrC understands the rule which people have so fervently been shouting to know that next time, which did occur, they would act accordinging, and so far have done so.<br>
<br>
Both Ogermeister and Vsalrhal have been insulted personally in the recent flames for actions they took and &quot;l00t&quot; they achieved, yet very few people can truly say that &quot;they want to get to the high end game&quot; merely to do so, and that loot means nothing.  Look at Hastley, he could be attributed as one of those rare people but who else.<br>
<br>
Sure...perhaps it wasnt the best idea for Oger to join and then quit after getting loot, but its not like he wouldnt have quit had he got none, it's just circumstance.  Same with Vsal, circumstances.<br>
<br>
It would be good for everyone to at least act why people act a certain way and perhaps say, &quot;Vsal/Oger, why did you blah blah?&quot;  And perhaps when you know the truth you wouldnt be so venemous with untruths, if they happen to be so.<br>
<br>
I enjoy reading the flame boards and believe that in certain times they are good, well written documents that describe the errors of people/guilds and in such are fun to read.  As a common necessity of human nature is the need/want to see others fail for where they make mistakes hopefully others wont, and you can achieve more through learning mistakes.<br>
<br>
Hopefully this is the case here. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2045.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2045.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2045.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2045.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a> <b>5</b> <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2045.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2045.topic&start=121&stop=140>7</a><a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2045.topic&start=141&stop=160>8</a><a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2045.topic&start=161&stop=180>9</a><a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2045.topic&start=181&stop=200>10</a><a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2045.topic&start=201&stop=220>11</a><a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2045.topic&start=221&stop=221>12</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showPrevMessage?topicID=2045.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showNextMessage?topicID=2045.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2045.topic&index=100><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/fr/themes/default/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub28.ezb